  06 Feb 2009; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org>
  qt-core-4.5.0_beta1.ebuild, qt-core-4.5.0_rc1.ebuild,
  qt-core-4.9999.ebuild:
  Moving qdoc3 installation on /usr/bin and make it independent from doc use
  flag

  23 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.5.0_beta1.ebuild,
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.9999.ebuild:
  
  Install qdoc3 with qt-core when doc flag is enabled. qdoc3 is required
  from some packages to generate documentation

  19 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.4.9999.ebuild,
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.9999.ebuild:
  Build adp_doc(html documentation) instead of full
  documentation(html+examples+qch) cause it will fails if there is no qt-gui
  installed on system.

  19 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.4.9999.ebuild:
  Removing non-existing target (bootstrap) which made qt-core to build
  useless projects

  17 Jan 2009; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> qt-core-4.5.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Add keywords as per 4.4.2 in official tree

  17 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.4.9999.ebuild,
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.9999.ebuild:
  Enabling glib,ssl flags by default

  17 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.4.9999.ebuild,
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.9999.ebuild:
  Fixing doc installation, using -xshape on ./configure to support drag and
  drop on Designer

  16 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.4.9999.ebuild:
  Added workarounds for html docs installation

  15 Jan 2009; Markos Chandras (hwoarang) <hwoarang@silverarrow.gr>
  +x11-libs/qt-core/qt-core-4.4.9999.ebuild:
  Adding qt-core-4.4.9999 ebuild

*qt-core-4.5.0_beta1 (13 Jan 2009)

